# AppBuilder has no local-only environment overrides yet — most vars are
# provided by the monorepo root .env.local / .env (loaded automatically by
# next.config.ts). Set app-only overrides here in an apps/appbuilder/.env.local
# if you need them.
#
# AppBuilder's own database, auth, and AI provider config ship in later
# milestones (M02, M03, M07) and will be documented here when they land.
